Changes with ngx-http-log-json 0.0.3                                31 Mar 2017

    *) allow to write to multiple destination with differente formats
    *) http_log_json_format and http_log_json_output directives separation
    *) significant overhaul for hiding json implementation
    *) re-factoring for allowing multiple destination/format

Changes with ngx-http-log-json 0.0.2                                26 Mar 2017

    *) upgrade to nginx 1.11.10 support
    *) parse recipe with pcre regex
    *) support literal boolean values
    *) support literal null values
    *) support array values
    *) refactoring functions
    *) unit tests
    *) travis script integration
    *) if= condition argument

